CARDBOX REPOSITORY
(Lesser GPL licence)

YOU NEED:
- Java 1.6
- Apache ant
- Apache maven


WHERE'S THE CARDBOX JAVA CODE?

Check ./projects/cardbox for all the server/client code


COMPILING THE CARDBOX

Check the Ant build script for most detailed info (./build.xml)

These probably work:
- Build the jar:
ant dist
- Run a test server (production-style mode):
ant server
- Copy the jar into your maven repository (might be garbage):
ant maven-deploy

